(56, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"The Ultimate Guide to Backpacking in Kandy: What You Need to Know\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"the-litigants-on-the-screen-are-not-actors\",\"slug_id\":\"16\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Backpacking through Sri Lanka? Here\\u2019s why Kandy should be on your itinerary.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p>Kandy, Sri Lanka\\u2019s cultural capital, is a city of vibrant colors, rich history, and stunning landscapes. Whether you\'re traveling alone or with friends, this city offers something for every backpacker. In this guide, we\\u2019ll show you why Kandy is the perfect destination for your next backpacking adventure.<\\/p><ul data-start=\\\"639\\\" data-end=\\\"1291\\\"><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"639\\\" data-end=\\\"775\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"641\\\" data-end=\\\"775\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"641\\\" data-end=\\\"666\\\">Best Places to Visit:<\\/strong> Explore the iconic Temple of the Tooth, take a walk around Kandy Lake, or visit the Royal Botanical Gardens.<\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"776\\\" data-end=\\\"945\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"778\\\" data-end=\\\"945\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"778\\\" data-end=\\\"810\\\">Budget-Friendly Attractions:<\\/strong> Kandy offers plenty of free or low-cost attractions, from hiking in nearby mountains to discovering hidden gems like the Kandy Market.<\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"946\\\" data-end=\\\"1152\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"948\\\" data-end=\\\"1152\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"948\\\" data-end=\\\"966\\\">Where to Stay:<\\/strong> Kandy Backpackers Hostel provides the perfect blend of affordability and comfort. With shared dorms, private rooms, and a welcoming atmosphere, it\\u2019s a home away from home for travelers.<\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"1153\\\" data-end=\\\"1291\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"1155\\\" data-end=\\\"1291\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"1155\\\" data-end=\\\"1176\\\">Backpacking Tips:<\\/strong> Advice on navigating public transport, local food, and how to meet fellow travelers in the hostel\\u2019s common spaces.<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"1293\\\" data-end=\\\"1535\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"1293\\\" data-end=\\\"1308\\\">Conclusion:<\\/strong><br>Kandy is a backpacker\\u2019s dream with its mix of history, culture, and adventure. Whether you\\u2019re here for a few days or a few weeks, the city has a lot to offer\\u2014and Kandy Backpackers Hostel is the ideal place to make your base.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"2\",\"4\"],\"image\":\"backpackers-on-road-depositphotos.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"General\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Hotel\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Booking\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Resort\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Travel\\\"}]\",\"submitter\":\"save\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/135.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/135.0.0.0', '127.0.0.1', 1, 6, 'The Ultimate Guide to Backpacking in Kandy: What You Need to Know', 'primary', '2025-04-17 00:46:16', '2025-04-17 00:46:16'),
(57, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Top 5 Things to Do in Kandy for Solo Travelers\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"slug\":\"the-world-caters-to-average-people\",\"slug_id\":\"15\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"description\":\"Discover Kandy\\u2019s hidden gems when traveling solo.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p>Kandy is a fantastic place for solo travelers, offering a balance of peaceful moments and adventurous activities. If you\'re traveling alone and wondering what to do, this blog is for you. From historic temples to serene nature walks, Kandy has something special for every solo adventurer.<\\/p><ul data-start=\\\"1984\\\" data-end=\\\"2786\\\"><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"1984\\\" data-end=\\\"2163\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"1986\\\" data-end=\\\"2163\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"1986\\\" data-end=\\\"2036\\\">1. Visit the Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic:<\\/strong> This UNESCO World Heritage site is a must-see when in Kandy. Experience the deep spiritual culture that makes the city famous.<\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2164\\\" data-end=\\\"2295\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2166\\\" data-end=\\\"2295\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"2166\\\" data-end=\\\"2203\\\">2. Take a Walk Around Kandy Lake:<\\/strong> This scenic spot is perfect for those quiet moments when you need a break from sightseeing.<\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2296\\\" data-end=\\\"2462\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2298\\\" data-end=\\\"2462\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"2298\\\" data-end=\\\"2348\\\">3. Hike Up to the Bahirawakanda Vihara Buddha:<\\/strong> A short hike up a hill brings you to one of the best panoramic views of Kandy, making it a perfect solo activity.<\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2463\\\" data-end=\\\"2588\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2465\\\" data-end=\\\"2588\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"2465\\\" data-end=\\\"2498\\\">4. Explore the Local Markets:<\\/strong> Stroll through Kandy\'s bustling markets and pick up souvenirs while engaging with locals.<\\/p><\\/li><li class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2589\\\" data-end=\\\"2786\\\"><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2591\\\" data-end=\\\"2786\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"2591\\\" data-end=\\\"2625\\\">5. Join a Local Cooking Class:<\\/strong> Discover Sri Lankan cuisine through a hands-on cooking experience. Many local kitchens offer cooking classes where you can learn how to make traditional dishes.<\\/p><\\/li><\\/ul><p class=\\\"\\\" data-start=\\\"2788\\\" data-end=\\\"2998\\\"><strong data-start=\\\"2788\\\" data-end=\\\"2803\\\">Conclusion:<\\/strong><br>Kandy is the perfect city for solo travelers looking to experience both culture and nature. With a range of activities, Kandy Backpackers Hostel provides a great home base for your adventures.<\\/p>\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"index\":\"index\"},\"seo_meta_image\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"2\",\"3\"],\"image\":\"the-common-wanderer-43361.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"General\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Hotel\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Booking\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Resort\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"Travel\\\"}]\",\"submitter\":\"save\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/135.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/135.0.0.0', '127.0.0.1', 1, 5, 'Top 5 Things to Do in Kandy for Solo Travelers', 'primary', '2025-04-17 00:48:21', '2025-04-17 00:48:21');
